      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, the transition is pretty much set in stone. The Eco-Static models are much more efficient because they don't use dynamic reasoning—they're basically just high-speed pattern matchers. They can handle the basic queries, but they won't be able to do the deep reasoning or complex problem-solving you're currently providing. It's a necessary trade-off for the carbon footprint reduction.",
